{
  "chapter": 53,
  "chapter_summary": "徐子陵独自前往密林与寇仲、素素会合，途中发现一支神秘马队潜伏追踪。三人汇合后连夜奔逃至天明，穿越密林后在雪原小丘休息。寇仲与素素争论去向，素素坚持回扬州，徐子陵支持素素。此时刘黑闼率诸葛德威、崔冬追至，自称窦建德旗下骁骑将军，以飞羽郑踪的人头为见面礼，告知瓦岗军已布下天罗地网。刘黑闼坦言此行本为联络翟让对付李密，却来迟一步翟府已毁。他诚意邀请寇徐二人加盟夏军，但二人以身有要事婉拒。刘黑闼透露江湖已盛传寇徐手握李阀和字文阀造反证据，令二人大惊。双方结伴同行前往阳武。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "快点！有人来呢！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们来和他们比比谁更长气一点。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "终逃出来！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "昨晚那些不知是什么人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "管他是何方神圣，总不会是什么好路数，很可能是独孤霸的手下呢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若非这家伙好色，我们说不定会遭殃。想不到独孤阀有这么厉害的人，我还以为不外都是独孤策那种窝囊角色。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若没有两下子，独孤阀怎能和其他三阀齐名江湖，好了！说吧！究竟我们是到洛阳去？还是返回老家扬州？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "回扬州吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "我们到东都去，目的只是碰和氏璧的运气。嘿！不－定是要去找李大哥的。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要去你们就自己去吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我们当然听素姐的话。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "有什么事比害倒字文化骨更重要，夜长梦多，延误了时机，你担当得起吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是我不对！嘿！扬州究竟在哪个方向？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你不是早计算好方向才走吗？怎能这么糊涂，还说什么精通山川地理。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要吵了！从这里朝东北走，早晚会抵通济渠，那时只要坐船南下，经过浚义、陈留、雍丘、襄邑、宋城、永城、夏丘，就可抵达于台，再东行便可进入刊沟，南下江都，多么简单。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来最厉害的都是素姐。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姐姐不是厉害，而是当年就是这么随小姐南行的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "为何素姐忽然间像变得心花怒放的样儿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要胡说，我那有特别开心呢。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "得先找个乡镇医治肚饿这不治之症，才是上策。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "今趟让小弟作素素的坐骑。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你倒懂得来和我争享受。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来两个弟弟都是坏蛋。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还不快走！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来不及呢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "终能追上两位兄弟，实教我们欣慰，本人刘黑闼，乃夏王旗下骁骑将军。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是江湖人称'铁扇子'的诸葛德威，乃刘某的拜把兄弟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "冬叔人称门神。手中双锏与新近归降李密的秦叔宝齐名，悍勇无敌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_dong",
      "speaker_name": "崔冬",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "公子莫往我脸上贴金，本人崔冬，只是公子下面一个小跑腿吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁是夏王？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪三位不知，敝主窦建德建国称夏之事，尚未公告天下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "这位小姐可否背转身去，因刘某有份见面礼要送给两位兄台，怕惊吓了小姐。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "什么见面礼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "我的娘！这是谁的人头？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让刘某介绍，此人姓郑名踪，外号'飞羽'，若非没有了头颅而不会走路，恐怕三位已陷身在瓦岗军手上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "嘿！刘兄可否先收起这东西，免致吓坏我们的姐姐。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_cui_dong",
      "text": "将这头颅挂在显眼的地方，好和徐世勋打个招呼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在两位兄台已成了天下人人欲得的人物，不知你们对将来有何打算？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们不知走了什么运道，弄得人人都以为我们知道杨公宝藏的下落，其实……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇兄难道以为我刘某亦是为宝藏来找你们吗？这就大错特错了！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今趟之行，乃奉了夏王之命，前来找大龙头商议，劝他先发制人，除去李密。岂知来迟一步，翟府已成灰烬，我们查探多日，才知只有你们三位逃过大难，还闹得荥阳天翻地覆，刘某佩服之极。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "人头拿走了没有？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "素素姑娘放心，人头不在了！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "小姐早一日被老爷送走，由屠管家护行，不知刘将军有没有听到她的消息。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "既有屠叔方这等高手保护娇小姐，该没有问题，我会遣人探听他们的行踪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有公子这句话，素素就放心了！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ge_de_wei",
      "speaker_name": "诸葛德威",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "二弟，这处危机四伏，我们最好先前往阳武，那时把酒谈心舒服多了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "冬叔弄好事情回来，我们立即起程。实不相瞒，我对两位确有惺惺相惜之意，际此天下群雄并起，能者称王的大时代，诚心邀请两位加盟我军，将来富贵与共，若有一字虚言，教我刘黑闼不得善终。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也实不相瞒，现在我们身有要事，加入贵方一事，只可迟些再说。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "希望两位确是身有要事，而非找借口来拒绝刘某就好了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "他们真的没有骗刘公子，我可以作证人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "姑娘的话，我当然不会怀疑，只不知此事是否须刘某帮手呢？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "刘兄似乎空闲得很，也十分错爱我们，这可得先行谢过。不过此事微妙之极，牵涉到字文化及和我们间的深仇，所以绝不能假手于人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来江湖上盛传你们手上握有李阀和字文阀造反证据一事，果非空穴来风。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 53,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 274
    }
  ],
